                          <path d="M18 8h-1a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v8a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h1a2 2 0 0 0 2-2v-8a2 2 0 0 0-2-2z" />
                          <path d="M7 8H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v8a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h1" />
                        </svg><span>Feedback</span></div>
                      <p>Strong diagnostic instinct. Also verify replication state before eviction decisions.</p>
